/* CGGN$KEY_CLRFRM */
BEGIN
  clear_form;
  IF :SYSTEM.FORM_STATUS = 'CHANGED' THEN
    RAISE FORM_TRIGGER_FAILURE;
  END IF;
END;

END;

/* CGHP$CALL_HELP_FORM */
BEGIN
  :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := '';
  IF (:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE IS NULL) THEN
    qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(23, 'Falta el fichero de ayuda o es incorrecto'), 'W', 'OFG', 23);
  ELSE
    :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HPATH || '';
    BEGIN
      CGHP$CALL_MS_HELP(0 ,:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE);
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
  END IF;
END;

begin
  qms$event_form('KEY-HELP','AFTER');

/* CGYR$SET_DATE_FORMAT */
BEGIN
  set_application_property(DATE_FORMAT_COMPATIBILITY_MODE, '5.0');
  set_application_property(PLSQL_DATE_FORMAT, 'YYYY/MM/DD HH24:MI:SS');
  set_application_property(BUILTIN_DATE_FORMAT, 'YYYY/MM/DD HH24:MI:SS');
  forms_ddl('ALTER SESSION SET NLS_DATE_FORMAT = ''YYYY/MM/DD HH24:MI:SS''');
END;

/* CGNV$PRE_FORM_NAVCUR */
  DECLARE
  rg_id RECORDGROUP;
  gc_wnd GROUPCOLUMN;
  gc_item GROUPCOLUMN;
BEGIN
  CGNV$.nav_opening_wnd := FALSE;
  rg_id := create_group('CGNV$WINDOW_ITEM');
  gc_wnd := add_group_column(rg_id, 'WINDOW', CHAR_COLUMN, 80);
  gc_item := add_group_column(rg_id, 'ITEM', CHAR_COLUMN, 80);
  add_group_row(rg_id, 1);
  set_group_char_cell(gc_wnd, 1, 'CALENDAR');
  set_group_char_cell(gc_item, 1, 'CALENDAR.OK');
  add_group_row(rg_id, 2);
  set_group_char_cell(gc_wnd, 2, 'LIBROS');
  set_group_char_cell(gc_item, 2, 'CNTBNC.NOMBRE');
  add_group_row(rg_id, 3);
  set_group_char_cell(gc_wnd, 3, 'WINDOW');
  set_group_char_cell(gc_item, 3, 'CGNV$WINDOW_1.BTN_VER_COMPROBANTE');
END;

/* CGNV$PRE_FORM_NAVCCF */
  DECLARE
  rg_id RECORDGROUP;
  gc_type GROUPCOLUMN;
  gc_name GROUPCOLUMN;
  gc_parent GROUPCOLUMN;
  gc_tag GROUPCOLUMN;
  gc_extra GROUPCOLUMN;
BEGIN
  CGNV$.nav_close_forms := TRUE;
  CGNV$.nav_opening_wnd := FALSE;
  rg_id := create_group('CGSH$FORM_OBJECTS');
  gc_type := add_group_column(rg_id, 'OBJECT_TYPE', CHAR_COLUMN, 2);
  gc_name := add_group_column(rg_id, 'OBJECT_NAME', CHAR_COLUMN, 40);
  gc_parent := add_group_column(rg_id, 'PARENT_NAME', CHAR_COLUMN, 40);
  gc_tag := add_group_column(rg_id, 'ITEM_TAG', CHAR_COLUMN, 40);
  gc_extra := add_group_column(rg_id, 'EXTRA_TEXT', CHAR_COLUMN, 240);
  add_group_row(rg_id, 1);
  set_group_char_cell(gc_type, 1, 'WN');
  set_group_char_cell(gc_name, 1, 'CALENDAR');
  set_group_char_cell(gc_parent, 1, '');
  add_group_row(rg_id, 2);
  set_group_char_cell(gc_type, 2, 'WN');
  set_group_char_cell(gc_name, 2, 'LIBROS');
  set_group_char_cell(gc_parent, 2, '');
  add_group_row(rg_id, 3);
  set_group_char_cell(gc_type, 3, 'WN');
  set_group_char_cell(gc_name, 3, 'WINDOW');
  set_group_char_cell(gc_parent, 3, '');
  add_group_row(rg_id, 4);
  set_group_char_cell(gc_type, 4, 'WN');
  set_group_char_cell(gc_name, 4, 'QMS$HIDDEN_ITEMS');
  set_group_char_cell(gc_parent, 4, '');
END;

/* CGGN$GET_DATE_AND_USER */
BEGIN
  DECLARE
    CURSOR C IS
      select  SYSDATE, USER
      from    SYS.DUAL;
  BEGIN
    OPEN C;
    FETCH C
    into    :PARAMETER.CGU$SYSDATE, :PARAMETER.CGU$USER;
    IF COTFOUND THEN
      CLOSE C;
      qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(3, 'No hay ninguna fila en la tabla <p1>', 'SYS.DUAL' ), 'F', 'OFG', 3);
      qms$forms_errors.raise_failure;
    END IF;
    CLOSE C;
  END;
END;

/* CGAP$TES_SEQUENCE_BEFORE */
begin
  qms$event_form('WHEN-NEW-FORM-INSTANCE');
/*
 CREADO POR: Juan Carlos Cabrera
 PROPOSITO:  Maximizar la ventana principal y descapacitar el boton de impresión si no tiene
             un reporte asociado
 FECHA:      26/NOV/1999
*/
  SET_WINDOW_PROPERTY(FORMS_MDI_WINDOW,WINDOW_STATE,MAXIMIZE);
  IF :GLOBAL.CG$REPORTE IS NULL THEN
    QMS$TOOLBAR.HIDE_BUTTON('PRINT');
  END IF;
end;
/* CGGN$CALL_GENERATOR_CODE */
BEGIN
  CGBS2$.SET_COORD_STYLE( 'P' );
  CGBS2$.SET_QRY_ON_ENTRY( 'Y' );
  BEGIN
    CG$WHEN_NEW_FORM_INSTANCE;
  EXCEPTION
    WHEN OTHERS THEN
      CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
  END;
END;

BEGIN
   IF NOT GNRL.ROL_HABILITADO('INICIAR_BNC') THEN
      QMS$ERRORS.SHOW_DEBUG_INFO('NO ESTA HABILITADO');
      SET_ITEM_PROPERTY('FECHA_REAL',ENABLED,PROPERTY_FALSE);
      SET_ITEM_PROPERTY('FECHA_REAL',REQUIRED,PROPERTY_FALSE);
   ELSE
      SET_ITEM_PROPERTY('FECHA_REAL',REQUIRED,PROPERTY_TRUE);
   END IF;
END;

/* CGAP$TES_SEQUENCE_BEFORE */
begin
  qms$event_form('WHEN-WINDOW-ACTIVATED');
end;

BEGIN
SET_WINDOW_PROPERTY('LIBROS',WINDOW_STATE, MAXIMIZE);
END;
/* CGNV$WHEN_WINDOW_ACTIVATED */
BEGIN
  IF( (:SYSTEM.CURSOR_ITEM IS NOT NULL) AND
      (:SYSTEM.EVENT_WINDOW) !=
       CGNV$GET_ITEM_WINDOW(:SYSTEM.CURSOR_ITEM) ) THEN
    CGNV$.NAVIGATE_TO_WINDOW(:SYSTEM.EVENT_WINDOW);
  END IF;
END;
/* CGAP$TES_SEQUENCE_AFTER */
begin
  qms$event_form('WHEN-WINDOW-ACTIVATED','AFTER');
end;
   - Ejecutar en Modo de Ingreso de Consulta         Sí
   - Jerarquía de Ejecución                          Sustituir
   - Desplegar en 'Ayuda de Teclado'                 No
   - Texto de 'Ayuda de Teclado'

/* CGNV$NAVIGATE_PRVBLK */
BEGIN
  BEGIN
    CGNV$PREV_ITEM;
  EXCEPTION
    WHEN OTHERS THEN
      CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
  END;
END;

/* CGBS$ON_CLEAR_DETAILS */
BEGIN
  IF (FORM_FAILURE and :SYSTEM.COORDINATION_OPERATION in ('MOUSE', 'DUPLICATE_RECORD')) THEN
    RAISE FORM_TRIGGER_FAILURE;
  END IF;
  IF (:SYSTEM.MASTER_BLOCK = :SYSTEM.TRIGGER_BLOCK) THEN
    CGBS$.CLEAR_MASTER_DETAIL( :SYSTEM.MASTER_BLOCK, :SYSTEM.COORDINATION_OPERATION );
  END IF;
END;
   * Ejecutar en Modo de Ingreso de Consulta         No
   - Jerarquía de Ejecución                          Sustituir
   * Desplegar en 'Ayuda de Teclado'                 Sí
   - Texto de 'Ayuda de Teclado'                     
   - Pasos de Trigger                                
   ----------
   * Nombre                                          ON-POPULATE-DETAILS
   - Información de Subclase                         
   - Comentarios                                     
   - Estilo de Trigger                               PL/SQL
   * Texto de Trigger                                

/* CGBS$ON_POPULATE_DETAILS */
BEGIN
  CGBS$.QUERY_DETAILS( :SYSTEM.CURSOR_BLOCK, :GLOBAL.CG$QUERY_MODE );
END;
   * Ejecutar en Modo de Ingreso de Consulta         No
   - Jerarquía de Ejecución                          Sustituir
   * Desplegar en 'Ayuda de Teclado'                 Sí

/* CGBS$KEY_ENTQRY_FRM */
BEGIN
  IF (get_block_property( :SYSTEM.TRIGGER_BLOCK, QUERY_ALLOWED) = 'FALSE') THEN
    qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(37, 'Consulta no permitida en este bloque'), 'E', 'OFG', 37);
    qms$forms_errors.raise_failure;
  END IF;
  CGBS$.DO_KEYQRY( :SYSTEM.TRIGGER_BLOCK, 'ENTER_QUERY', :SYSTEM.MODE);
END;
   * Ejecutar en Modo de Ingreso de Consulta         Sí
   - Jerarquía de Ejecución                          Sustituir
   * Desplegar en 'Ayuda de Teclado'                 Sí
   - Texto de 'Ayuda de Teclado'                     
   - Pasos de Trigger                                
   ----------
   * Nombre                                          KEY-EXEQRY
   - Información de Subclase                         
   - Comentarios                                     
   - Estilo de Trigger                               PL/SQL
   * Texto de Trigger                                

/* CGBS$KEY_EXEQRY_FRM */
BEGIN
  IF (get_block_property( :SYSTEM.TRIGGER_BLOCK, QUERY_ALLOWED) = 'FALSE') THEN
    qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(37, 'Consulta no permitida en este bloque'), 'E', 'OFG', 37);
    qms$forms_errors.raise_failure;
  END IF;
  CGBS$.DO_KEYQRY( :SYSTEM.TRIGGER_BLOCK, 'EXECUTE_QUERY', :SYSTEM.MODE);
END;
   * Ejecutar en Modo de Ingreso de Consulta         Sí

   - Información de Subclase                         
   - Comentarios                                     
   - Estilo de Trigger                               PL/SQL
   * Texto de Trigger                                

/* CGBS$KEY_CLRBLK_FRM */
BEGIN
  IF ( CGBS2$.IS_RECORD_DIRTY(:SYSTEM.TRIGGER_BLOCK) ) THEN
    RAISE FORM_TRIGGER_FAILURE;
  END IF;
  IF (:SYSTEM.BLOCK_STATUS = 'CHANGED' or CGBS2$.IS_COMMIT_NEEDED( :SYSTEM.TRIGGER_BLOCK ) ) THEN
    CGBS2$.DO_COMMIT_DIALOGUE;
  END IF;
  clear_block( NO_VALIDATE );
END;
   * Ejecutar en Modo de Ingreso de Consulta         Sí
   - Jerarquía de Ejecución                          Sustituir
   * Desplegar en 'Ayuda de Teclado'                 Sí
   - Texto de 'Ayuda de Teclado'                     
   - Pasos de Trigger                                
   ----------
   * Nombre                                          KEY-CLRREC
   - Información de Subclase                         
   - Comentarios                                     
   - Estilo de Trigger                               PL/SQL
   * Texto de Trigger                                

/* CGBS$KEY_CLRREC */
BEGIN
  IF ( CGBS2$.IS_RECORD_DIRTY(:SYSTEM.TRIGGER_BLOCK) ) THEN
    RAISE FORM_TRIGGER_FAILURE;
  END IF;
  IF (:SYSTEM.BLOCK_STATUS = 'CHANGED' or CGBS2$.IS_COMMIT_NEEDED( :SYSTEM.TRIGGER_BLOCK ) ) THEN
    CGBS2$.DO_COMMIT_DIALOGUE;
  END IF;
  clear_record;
END;
   * Ejecutar en Modo de Ingreso de Consulta         Sí
   - Jerarquía de Ejecución                          Sustituir
   * Desplegar en 'Ayuda de Teclado'                 Sí
   - Texto de 'Ayuda de Teclado'

  qms$forms_errors.raise_failure;
END;

/* CGFK$QRY_LOOKUP_DATA */
BEGIN
  IF (name_in('CNTBNC.ENTFNC_CODIGO') IS NOT NULL) THEN
    BEGIN
      CGFK$QRY_CNTBNC_CNTBNC_ENTFNC_(:CNTBNC.NOMBRE ,:CNTBNC.ENTFNC_CODIGO);
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN NO_DATA_FOUND THEN
        qms$forms_errors.push('La entidad Financiera no existe', 'E', 'OFG', 0);
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
    SET_RECORD_PROPERTY(:SYSTEM.TRIGGER_RECORD, 'CNTBNC', STATUS ,                 QUERY_STATUS);
  END IF;
END;

/* CGFK$RESET_BLOCK_WHERE_CLAUSE */
BEGIN
  IF (CG$BNCINGLBR_GLOBALS.CNTBNC_WHERE <> 'first_time') THEN
    set_block_property('CNTBNC', DEFAULT_WHERE, CG$BNCINGLBR_GLOBALS.CNTBNC_WHERE);
    CG$BNCINGLBR_GLOBALS.CNTBNC_WHERE := 'first_time';
  END IF;
END;

     - Estilo de Trigger                             PL/SQL
     o Texto de Trigger                              

/* CGAP$OLES_SEQUENCE_BEFORE */
begin
   qms$event_data_block('PRE-QUERY');
end;
/* CGFK$DEFAULT_WHERE */
BEGIN
  DECLARE
    block_id   Block := find_block('CNTBNC');
    sub_where  VARCHAR2(4000) := NULL;
    def_where  VARCHAR2(4000) := NULL;
    r_string   VARCHAR2(512) := NULL;

    FUNCTION add_and(
      P_WHERE IN VARCHAR2
    ) RETURN VARCHAR2 IS
    BEGIN
      IF (nvl( length(P_WHERE), 0) != 0) THEN
        RETURN( P_WHERE || ' and ');
      ELSE
        RETURN( P_WHERE );
      END IF;
    END;

  BEGIN
    IF ( CG$BNCINGLBR_GLOBALS.CNTBNC_WHERE = 'first_time') THEN
      CG$BNCINGLBR_GLOBALS.CNTBNC_WHERE := get_block_property(block_id, DEFAULT_WHERE);
    END IF;
    def_where := CG$BNCINGLBR_GLOBALS.CNTBNC_WHERE;

    sub_where := NULL;
    r_string := NAME_IN('CNTBNC.NOMBRE');
    IF (r_string IS NOT NULL) THEN
      BEGIN
        IF substr(r_string, 1,1) in ('<','>','=') THEN
          sub_where := add_and( sub_where ) || '(NOMBRE '|| r_string || ')';
        ELSIF substr(r_string, 1,1) ='#' THEN
          sub_where := add_and( sub_where ) || '(NOMBRE '|| substr(r_string,2) || ')';
        ELSIF instr(r_string, '') <> 0 THEN
          sub_where := add_and( sub_where ) || '(NOMBRE like '''|| replace(r_string,'''','''''') || ''')';
        ELSE
          sub_where := add_and( sub_where ) || '(NOMBRE ='''|| replace(r_string,'''','''''') || ''')';
        END IF;
      END;
    END IF;
    IF (sub_where IS NOT NULL) THEN
      def_where := add_and( def_where ) || '((ENTFNC_CODIGO) in '||'(select CODIGO '||'from ENTIDADES_FINANCIERAS where '|| sub_where || '))';
    END IF;

    set_block_property(block_id, DEFAULT_WHERE, def_where);

  EXCEPTION
    WHEN VALUE_ERROR THEN
      qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(33, 'Los criterios de consulta son demasiado complejos. Simplifíquelos y vuelva a realizar la consulta.'), 'E', 'OFG', 33);
      qms$forms_errors.raise_failure;
  END;
END;

     - Comentarios                                   
     - Estilo de Trigger                             PL/SQL
     * Texto de Trigger                              

/* CGTE$BLK_LEVEL_ERROR_TRAP */
BEGIN
  DECLARE
    err_code        CONSTANT NUMBER         := ERROR_CODE;
    err_type        CONSTANT VARCHAR2(3)    := ERROR_TYPE;
    server_err               NUMBER         := abs(DBMS_ERROR_CODE);
    server_msg               VARCHAR2(2000) := DBMS_ERROR_TEXT;
    constraint_name          VARCHAR2(61);
  BEGIN
    IF (err_type = 'FRM' and
        err_code in (40506, 40508, 40509, 40510) ) THEN

      WHILE (server_err = 604) LOOP
        CGTE$POP_ERROR_STACK(server_err, server_msg);
      END LOOP;

      IF ( CGTE$CHECK_CONSTRAINT_VIO(server_err, server_msg) ) THEN
        QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.RAISE_FAILURE;
      END IF;

      constraint_name := CGTE$STRIP_CONSTRAINT(server_msg);

    END IF;

    IF (err_type = 'FRM' and
        err_code = 40735 ) THEN


      WHILE (server_err = 604) LOOP
        CGTE$POP_ERROR_STACK(server_err, server_msg);
      END LOOP;

      qms$forms_errors.push(err_type||'-'||to_char(server_err)||': '||server_msg, 'I', 'OFG', 0);
      qms$forms_errors.raise_failure;
    END IF;

    qms$forms_errors.push(err_type||'-'||to_char(err_code)||': '||ERROR_TEXT, 'I', 'OFG', 0);
    qms$forms_errors.raise_failure;

  END;
END;
     * Ejecutar en Modo de Ingreso de Consulta       Sí
     * Jerarquía de Ejecución                        Antes
     * Desplegar en 'Ayuda de Teclado'               Sí
     - Texto de 'Ayuda de Teclado'                   
     - Pasos de Trigger                              
     ----------
     * Nombre                                        KEY-HELP
     - Información de Subclase                       
     - Comentarios                                   
     - Estilo de Trigger                             PL/SQL
     * Texto de Trigger                              

/* CGHP$CALL_HELP_FORM */
BEGIN
  :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := '';
  IF (:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE IS NULL) THEN
    qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(23, 'Falta el fichero de ayuda o es incorrecto'), 'W', 'OFG', 23);
  ELSE
    :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HPATH || '';
    BEGIN
      CGHP$CALL_MS_HELP(0 ,:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE);
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
  END IF;
  :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := '';
  IF (:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE IS NULL) THEN
    qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(23, 'Falta el fichero de ayuda o es incorrecto'), 'W', 'OFG', 23);
  ELSE
    :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HPATH || '';
    BEGIN
      CGHP$CALL_MS_HELP(0 ,:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE);
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
  END IF;
END;

/* CGHP$CALL_HELP_FORM */
BEGIN
  :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := '';
  IF (:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE IS NULL) THEN
    qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(23, 'Falta el fichero de ayuda o es incorrecto'), 'W', 'OFG', 23);
  ELSE
    :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HPATH || '';
    BEGIN
      CGHP$CALL_MS_HELP(0 ,:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE);
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
  END IF;
END;

    qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(23, 'Falta el fichero de ayuda o es incorrecto'), 'W', 'OFG', 23);

    :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HPATH || '';
    BEGIN
      CGHP$CALL_MS_HELP(0 ,:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE);
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
  END IF;
END;

/* CGFK$QRY_LOOKUP_DATA */
BEGIN
  IF (name_in('LBR.TPOMVM_CODIGO') IS NOT NULL) THEN
    BEGIN
      CGFK$QRY_LBR_LBR_TPOMVM_FK(:LBR.ESTADO_DE_DISPONIBILIDAD ,:LBR.INGRESA_REFERENCIA ,:LBR.CONTABILIZACION ,:LBR.APLICABLE ,:LBR.OPERACION ,:LBR.TPOMVM_CODIGO);

      WHEN NO_DATA_FOUND THEN
        qms$forms_errors.push('El tipo de movimiento no existe', 'E', 'OFG', 0);
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
    SET_RECORD_PROPERTY(:SYSTEM.TRIGGER_RECORD, 'LBR', STATUS ,                 QUERY_STATUS);
  END IF;
END;

BEGIN
-- Conforma la lista de datos
DECLARE
NUM_REGISTRO NUMBER;
BEGIN
  qms$forms_errors.Add_Suppress_Message('FRM-40102');
  IF :SYSTEM.RECORD_STATUS IN ('INSERT','NEW') THEN
     IF :LBR.TPOMVM_CODIGO = 'BIN'  THEN
        CONFORMAR_LISTA;
        FIJA_VENTANA_TIPO;
        SET_ITEM_PROPERTY('MOV_TIPO',POSITION,0,0);
        SET_ITEM_PROPERTY('MOV_TIPO',WIDTH,1.328);
        SHOW_VIEW('CG$POPUP_1');
        GO_ITEM('MOV_TIPO');
     END IF;
  ELSE
     HIDE_VIEW('CG$POPUP_1');
     GO_ITEM('TPOMVM_CODIGO');
  END IF;
  qms$forms_errors.Delete_Suppress_Message('FRM-40102');
EXCEPTION
WHEN OTHERS THEN
   QMS$ERRORS.UNHANDLED_EXCEPTION ('Falló otra vez'|| SQLERRM);
END;
END;

/* CGFK$CLR_FK_ON_INS */

    BEGIN

    EXCEPTION

        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
  END IF;
END;

/* CGUI$GET_UNIQUE_ID */
BEGIN
  IF (name_in('LBR.NUMERO') IS NULL) THEN
    BEGIN
      CGUI$GET_NEXT_LBR_SEQ(:LBR.NUMERO);
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN NO_DATA_FOUND THEN
        qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(3, 'No hay ninguna fila en la tabla <p1>', 'SYS.DUAL' ), 'F', 'OFG', 3);
        qms$forms_errors.raise_failure;
      WHEN TOO_MANY_ROWS THEN
        qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(24, 'Hay más de una fila en la tabla <p1>', 'SYS.DUAL' ), 'F', 'OFG', 24);
        qms$forms_errors.raise_failure;
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
  END IF;
END;

/* CGWH$SET_AUDIT_INS_FLDS */
BEGIN
  :LBR.USUARIO_CREA := :PARAMETER.CGU$USER;
END;

BEGIN
--   :LBR.TPOMVM_CODIGO:= :TIPO.MOV_TIPO;
   IF :LBR.TPOMVM_CODIGO IS NOT NULL AND :LBR.TPOMVM_CODIGO = 'BIN' THEN
      QMS$ERRORS.SHOW_MESSAGE('BNC-00012');
   END IF;
   IF :LBR.FECHA_REAL IS NULL THEN
      :LBR.FECHA_REAL := :LBR.FECHA;
   END IF;
   IF :LBR.ESTADO = 'A' THEN
     IF :LBR.FECHA < SYSDATE-60 AND NOT GNRL.ROL_HABILITADO('ADMIN') THEN
        QMS$ERRORS.SHOW_MESSAGE('BNC-00025',TO_CHAR(SYSDATE-60,'DD/MM/YYYY'));
     END IF;
   END IF;
   IF :LBR.FECHA < SYSDATE-60 AND NOT GNRL.ROL_HABILITADO('ADMIN')THEN
      QMS$ERRORS.SHOW_MESSAGE('BNC-00025',TO_CHAR(SYSDATE-60,'DD/MM/YYYY'));
   END IF;
END;

/* CGGN$KEY_DUPREC */

  duplicate_record;
  BEGIN
    CG$CHK_PACKAGE_FAILURE;
  EXCEPTION
    WHEN OTHERS THEN
      CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
  END;

     * Nombre                                        ON-ERROR
     - Información de Subclase                       
     - Comentarios                                   
     - Estilo de Trigger                             PL/SQL
     * Texto de Trigger                              

/* CGTE$BLK_LEVEL_ERROR_TRAP */
BEGIN
  DECLARE
    err_code        CONSTANT NUMBER         := ERROR_CODE;
    err_type        CONSTANT VARCHAR2(3)    := ERROR_TYPE;
    server_err               NUMBER         := abs(DBMS_ERROR_CODE);
    server_msg               VARCHAR2(2000) := DBMS_ERROR_TEXT;
    constraint_name          VARCHAR2(61);
  BEGIN
    IF (err_type = 'FRM' and
        err_code in (40506, 40508, 40509, 40510) ) THEN

      WHILE (server_err = 604) LOOP
        CGTE$POP_ERROR_STACK(server_err, server_msg);
      END LOOP;

      IF ( CGTE$CHECK_CONSTRAINT_VIO(server_err, server_msg) ) THEN
        QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.RAISE_FAILURE;
      END IF;

      constraint_name := CGTE$STRIP_CONSTRAINT(server_msg);

      IF (server_err = 2291) THEN
        IF (constraint_name = 'LBR_TPOMVM_FK') THEN
          qms$forms_errors.push('El tipo de movimiento no existe', 'E', 'OFG', 0);
        ELSIF (constraint_name = 'LBR_TPOCMPEMP_FK') THEN
          qms$forms_errors.push('El tipo de Comprobante no existe', 'E', 'OFG', 0);
        ELSIF (constraint_name = 'LBR_CNTMVMBNC_FK') THEN
          qms$forms_errors.push('La Contabilización del movimiento no existe', 'E', 'OFG', 0);
        ELSIF (constraint_name = 'LBR_CNTBNC_FK') THEN
          qms$forms_errors.push('La cueta no existe', 'E', 'OFG', 0);
        ELSE
          qms$forms_errors.push(server_msg, 'I', 'OFG', 0);
        END IF;
        QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.RAISE_FAILURE;
      END IF;

      IF (server_err = 2292) THEN
        IF (err_code = 40509) THEN
          qms$forms_errors.push(server_msg, 'I', 'OFG', 0);
        END IF;
        QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.RAISE_FAILURE;
      END IF;
    END IF;

    IF (err_type = 'FRM' and
        err_code in (41105, 41106) ) THEN
      IF (err_code = 41105) THEN
      qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(35, 'La consulta de <p1> debe estar en el contexto de <p2>', 'Libros','Cuentas Bancarias' ), 'E', 'OFG', 35);
      qms$forms_errors.raise_failure;
    ELSIF (err_code = 41106) THEN
      qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(36, 'La inserción de <p1> debe estar en el contexto de <p2>', 'Libros','Cuentas Bancarias' ), 'E', 'OFG', 36);
      qms$forms_errors.raise_failure;
      END IF;
    END IF;

    IF (err_type = 'FRM' and
        err_code = 40735 ) THEN


      WHILE (server_err = 604) LOOP
        CGTE$POP_ERROR_STACK(server_err, server_msg);
      END LOOP;

      qms$forms_errors.push(err_type||'-'||to_char(server_err)||': '||server_msg, 'I', 'OFG', 0);
      qms$forms_errors.raise_failure;
    END IF;

    qms$forms_errors.push(err_type||'-'||to_char(err_code)||': '||ERROR_TEXT, 'I', 'OFG', 0);
    qms$forms_errors.raise_failure;

  END;
END;
     * Ejecutar en Modo de Ingreso de Consulta       Sí
     * Jerarquía de Ejecución                        Antes
     * Desplegar en 'Ayuda de Teclado'               Sí
     - Texto de 'Ayuda de Teclado'                   
     - Pasos de Trigger                              
     ----------
     * Nombre                                        KEY-HELP
     - Información de Subclase                       
     - Comentarios                                   
     - Estilo de Trigger                             PL/SQL
     * Texto de Trigger                              

/* CGHP$CALL_HELP_FORM */
BEGIN
  :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := '';
  IF (:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE IS NULL) THEN
    qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(23, 'Falta el fichero de ayuda o es incorrecto'), 'W', 'OFG', 23);
  ELSE
    :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HPATH || '';
    BEGIN
      CGHP$CALL_MS_HELP(0 ,:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE);
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
  END IF;
  :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := '';
  IF (:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE IS NULL) THEN
    qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(23, 'Falta el fichero de ayuda o es incorrecto'), 'W', 'OFG', 23);
  ELSE
    :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HPATH || '';
    BEGIN
      CGHP$CALL_MS_HELP(0 ,:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE);
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
  END IF;
  :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := '';
  IF (:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE IS NULL) THEN
    qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(23, 'Falta el fichero de ayuda o es incorrecto'), 'W', 'OFG', 23);
  ELSE
    :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HPATH || '';
    BEGIN
      CGHP$CALL_MS_HELP(0 ,:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE);
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
  END IF;
  :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := '';
  IF (:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE IS NULL) THEN
    qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(23, 'Falta el fichero de ayuda o es incorrecto'), 'W', 'OFG', 23);
  ELSE
    :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HPATH || '';
    BEGIN
      CGHP$CALL_MS_HELP(0 ,:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE);
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
  END IF;
END;
     * Ejecutar en Modo de Ingreso de Consulta       Sí
     * Jerarquía de Ejecución                        Antes
     * Desplegar en 'Ayuda de Teclado'               Sí
     - Texto de 'Ayuda de Teclado'                   
     - Pasos de Trigger                              
     ----------
     * Nombre                                        POST-UPDATE
     - Información de Subclase                       
     - Comentarios                                   
     - Estilo de Trigger                             PL/SQL
     * Texto de Trigger                              

BEGIN  -- Llama al proceso que contabiliza los Egresos de Activos Fijos
IF :LBR.LBR_IND = 'C' THEN
BEGIN
   CNTINT2.CONTABILIZAR_MOV_BANCARIOS(0,:LBR.NUMERO,:GLOBAL.TIPO_DE_CAMBIO,:GLOBAL.TIPO_DE_CAMBIOE,
   :GLOBAL.MONEDA_LOCAL,:GLOBAL.CG$EMPRESA_CODIGO,:LBR.CMP_TIPO,:LBR.CMP_FECHA,
   :LBR.CMP_CLAVE,:LBR.TPOMVM_CODIGO||:CNTBNC.TIPO||:CNTBNC.NUMERO);
EXCEPTION
WHEN OTHERS THEN
   :LBR.LBR_IND := 'E';
   QMS$ERRORS.UNHANDLED_EXCEPTION ('Falló el Proceso de Contabilización '|| SQLERRM);
END;
SET_APPLICATION_PROPERTY(CURSOR_STYLE,'DEFAULT');
END IF;
END;
     * Ejecutar en Modo de Ingreso de Consulta       No

BEGIN
   IF :LBR.ESTADO = 'A' THEN
     IF :LBR.FECHA < SYSDATE-60 AND NOT GNRL.ROL_HABILITADO('ADMIN') THEN
        QMS$ERRORS.SHOW_MESSAGE('BNC-00025',TO_CHAR(SYSDATE-60,'DD/MM/YYYY'));
     END IF;
   END IF;
   IF :LBR.FECHA < SYSDATE-60 AND NOT GNRL.ROL_HABILITADO('ADMIN')THEN
      QMS$ERRORS.SHOW_MESSAGE('BNC-00025',TO_CHAR(SYSDATE-60,'DD/MM/YYYY'));
   END IF;
END;

/* CGHP$CALL_HELP_FORM */
BEGIN
  :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := '';

    qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(23, 'Falta el fichero de ayuda o es incorrecto'), 'W', 'OFG', 23);

    :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HPATH || '';
    BEGIN
      CGHP$CALL_MS_HELP(0 ,:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE);
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
  END IF;
END;

/* CGBG$WHEN_NEW_ITEM_INSTANCE */
BEGIN
  next_item;
END;

/* CGHP$CALL_HELP_FORM */
BEGIN
  :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := '';
  IF (:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE IS NULL) THEN
    qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(23, 'Falta el fichero de ayuda o es incorrecto'), 'W', 'OFG', 23);
  ELSE
    :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HPATH || '';
    BEGIN
      CGHP$CALL_MS_HELP(0 ,:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE);
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
  END IF;
END;

/* CGFK$WVI_CLR_DEPS_OVF */
BEGIN
  IF (name_in('LBR.CNTBNC_EMP_CODIGO') IS NULL AND name_in('LBR.CMP_TIPO') IS NULL) THEN
    IF (:SYSTEM.RECORD_STATUS = 'NEW') THEN
      RETURN;
    END IF;
    BEGIN
      CGSF$CLRLU_LBR_LBR_TPOCMPEMP_F;
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
  END IF;
END;
       * Ejecutar en Modo de Ingreso de Consulta     No
       * Jerarquía de Ejecución                      Antes
       * Desplegar en 'Ayuda de Teclado'             Sí
       - Texto de 'Ayuda de Teclado'                 
       - Pasos de Trigger                            
       ----------
       * Nombre                                      KEY-HELP
       - Información de Subclase                     
       - Comentarios                                 
       - Estilo de Trigger                           PL/SQL
       * Texto de Trigger

/* CGFK$WVI_CLR_DEPS_OVF */
BEGIN
  IF (name_in('LBR.TPOMVM_CODIGO') IS NULL) THEN
    IF (:SYSTEM.RECORD_STATUS = 'NEW') THEN
      RETURN;
    END IF;
    BEGIN
      CGSF$CLRLU_LBR_LBR_TPOMVM_FK;
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
  END IF;
END;

/* CGUV$CHK_KEYS_ON_VAL_FLD */
BEGIN
      IF (    name_in('LBR.CMP_FECHA') IS NOT NULL
          OR name_in('LBR.CNTBNC_TIPO') IS NOT NULL
          OR name_in('LBR.ESTADO') IS NOT NULL
          OR name_in('LBR.CNTBNC_NUMERO') IS NOT NULL
          OR name_in('LBR.TPOMVM_CODIGO') IS NOT NULL
          OR name_in('LBR.FECHA') IS NOT NULL
          OR name_in('LBR.DEBE') IS NOT NULL
          OR name_in('LBR.HABER') IS NOT NULL
          OR name_in('LBR.DESCRIPCION') IS NOT NULL
          OR name_in('LBR.NUMERO_DOCUMENTO') IS NOT NULL
          OR name_in('LBR.CMP_TIPO') IS NOT NULL
          OR name_in('LBR.CMP_CLAVE') IS NOT NULL
          OR name_in('LBR.CNTBNC_EMP_CODIGO') IS NOT NULL) THEN
  IF (    name_in('LBR.CMP_FECHA') IS NOT NULL
      AND name_in('LBR.ESTADO') IS NOT NULL
      AND name_in('LBR.TPOMVM_CODIGO') IS NOT NULL
      AND name_in('LBR.FECHA') IS NOT NULL
      AND name_in('LBR.DEBE') IS NOT NULL
      AND name_in('LBR.HABER') IS NOT NULL
      AND name_in('LBR.DESCRIPCION') IS NOT NULL
      AND name_in('LBR.NUMERO_DOCUMENTO') IS NOT NULL
      AND name_in('LBR.CMP_TIPO') IS NOT NULL
      AND name_in('LBR.CMP_CLAVE') IS NOT NULL) THEN
  BEGIN
    CGUV$CHK_LBR_UK(
      :LBR.CMP_CLAVE
     ,:LBR.CMP_TIPO
     ,:LBR.NUMERO_DOCUMENTO
     ,:LBR.DESCRIPCION
     ,:LBR.HABER
     ,:LBR.DEBE
     ,:LBR.FECHA
     ,:LBR.ESTADO
     ,:LBR.CMP_FECHA
     ,:LBR.CNTBNC_TIPO
     ,:LBR.CNTBNC_NUMERO
     ,:LBR.CNTBNC_EMP_CODIGO
     ,:LBR.NUMERO
     ,:LBR.TPOMVM_CODIGO
     ,:SYSTEM.RECORD_STATUS );
    qms$forms_errors.push('Ya existe un momimiento  igual en el libro de Bancos', 'W', 'OFG', 0);
  EXCEPTION
    WHEN NO_DATA_FOUND THEN NULL;
    WHEN OTHERS THEN
      CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
  END;
  END IF;
      ELSE
        RAISE NO_DATA_FOUND;
      END IF;
END;
       * Ejecutar en Modo de Ingreso de Consulta     No
       * Jerarquía de Ejecución                      Antes
       * Desplegar en 'Ayuda de Teclado'             Sí
       - Texto de 'Ayuda de Teclado'                 
       - Pasos de Trigger                            
       ----------
       * Nombre                                      KEY-HELP
       - Información de Subclase                     
       - Comentarios                                 
       - Estilo de Trigger                           PL/SQL
       * Texto de Trigger

     ^ Estilo de Fuente                              Plano
     ^ Espaciado de Fuente                           Normal
     ^ Color de Primer Plano                         black
     ^ Color de Fondo                                white
     ^ Completar Patrón                              transparent
     ^ Atributo Lógico de Modo de Caracter           default
     ^ Blanco sobre Negro                            No

     - Estilo de Despliegue de Prompt                Primer Registro
     - Justificación de Prompt                       Inicio
     * Orilla de Adjunto de Prompt                   Arriba
     - Alineación de Prompt                          Inicio

     - Compensación de Alineación de Prompt          0

     ^ Tamaño de Fuente de Prompt                    8
     ^ Peso de Fuente de Prompt                      Mediano
     ^ Estilo de Fuente de Prompt                    Plano
     ^ Espaciado de Fuente de Prompt                 Normal
     ^ Valor de Primer Plano de Prompt               black
     * Indicio                                       Fecha
     ^ Desplegar Indicio Automáticamente             No

     ^ Grupo de Atributos Visuales de Consejos de Uso de HerramientasQMS$TOOLTIP

/* CGAP$OLES_SEQUENCE_BEFORE */
begin
   qms$calendar.key_listval;
end;
       - Ejecutar en Modo de Ingreso de Consulta     Sí
       - Jerarquía de Ejecución                      Sustituir
       - Desplegar en 'Ayuda de Teclado'             No
       - Texto de 'Ayuda de Teclado'                 
       - Pasos de Trigger                            
       ----------
       * Nombre                                      WHEN-VALIDATE-ITEM
       - Información de Subclase                     
       - Comentarios                                 
       - Estilo de Trigger                           PL/SQL
       * Texto de Trigger                            

BEGIN
-- Valida que la fecha del movimiento no sea menor a la fecha de apertura de cuenta
-- y que no sea menor que 2 meses.
   IF :LBR.FECHA IS NOT NULL THEN
      IF :LBR.FECHA < :CNTBNC.FECHA_APERTURA THEN
         :LBR.FECHA:= NULL;
         QMS$ERRORS.SHOW_MESSAGE('BNC-00023');
      ELSIF :LBR.FECHA < SYSDATE-60  AND NOT GNRL.ROL_HABILITADO('ADMIN') THEN
         QMS$ERRORS.SHOW_MESSAGE('No puede ingresar un movimiento con fecha inferor a '||TO_CHAR(SYSDATE-60,'DD/MM/YYYY'));
      END IF;
   END IF;
END;
/* CGUV$CHK_KEYS_ON_VAL_FLD */
BEGIN
        IF (    name_in('LBR.CMP_FECHA') IS NOT NULL
            OR name_in('LBR.CNTBNC_TIPO') IS NOT NULL
            OR name_in('LBR.ESTADO') IS NOT NULL
            OR name_in('LBR.CNTBNC_NUMERO') IS NOT NULL
            OR name_in('LBR.TPOMVM_CODIGO') IS NOT NULL
            OR name_in('LBR.FECHA') IS NOT NULL
            OR name_in('LBR.DEBE') IS NOT NULL
            OR name_in('LBR.HABER') IS NOT NULL
            OR name_in('LBR.DESCRIPCION') IS NOT NULL
            OR name_in('LBR.NUMERO_DOCUMENTO') IS NOT NULL
            OR name_in('LBR.CMP_TIPO') IS NOT NULL
            OR name_in('LBR.CMP_CLAVE') IS NOT NULL
            OR name_in('LBR.CNTBNC_EMP_CODIGO') IS NOT NULL) THEN
  IF (    name_in('LBR.CMP_FECHA') IS NOT NULL
      AND name_in('LBR.ESTADO') IS NOT NULL
      AND name_in('LBR.TPOMVM_CODIGO') IS NOT NULL
      AND name_in('LBR.FECHA') IS NOT NULL
      AND name_in('LBR.DEBE') IS NOT NULL
      AND name_in('LBR.HABER') IS NOT NULL
      AND name_in('LBR.DESCRIPCION') IS NOT NULL
      AND name_in('LBR.NUMERO_DOCUMENTO') IS NOT NULL
      AND name_in('LBR.CMP_TIPO') IS NOT NULL
      AND name_in('LBR.CMP_CLAVE') IS NOT NULL) THEN
  BEGIN
    CGUV$CHK_LBR_UK(
      :LBR.CMP_CLAVE
     ,:LBR.CMP_TIPO
     ,:LBR.NUMERO_DOCUMENTO
     ,:LBR.DESCRIPCION
     ,:LBR.HABER
     ,:LBR.DEBE
     ,:LBR.FECHA
     ,:LBR.ESTADO
     ,:LBR.CMP_FECHA
     ,:LBR.CNTBNC_TIPO
     ,:LBR.CNTBNC_NUMERO
     ,:LBR.CNTBNC_EMP_CODIGO
     ,:LBR.NUMERO
     ,:LBR.TPOMVM_CODIGO
     ,:SYSTEM.RECORD_STATUS );
    qms$forms_errors.push('Ya existe un momimiento  igual en el libro de Bancos', 'W', 'OFG', 0);
  EXCEPTION
    WHEN NO_DATA_FOUND THEN NULL;
    WHEN OTHERS THEN
      CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
  END;
  END IF;
        ELSE
          RAISE NO_DATA_FOUND;
        END IF;
END;
       * Ejecutar en Modo de Ingreso de Consulta     No
       * Jerarquía de Ejecución                      Sustituir
       * Desplegar en 'Ayuda de Teclado'             Sí
       - Texto de 'Ayuda de Teclado'                 
       - Pasos de Trigger                            
       ----------
       * Nombre                                      KEY-HELP
       - Información de Subclase                     
       - Comentarios                                 
       - Estilo de Trigger                           PL/SQL
       * Texto de Trigger                            

/* CGHP$CALL_HELP_FORM */
BEGIN
  :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := '';
  IF (:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE IS NULL) THEN
    qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(23, 'Falta el fichero de ayuda o es incorrecto'), 'W', 'OFG', 23);
  ELSE
    :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HPATH || '';
    BEGIN
      CGHP$CALL_MS_HELP(0 ,:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE);
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
  END IF;
END;

     ,:LBR.TPOMVM_CODIGO

    qms$forms_errors.push('Ya existe un momimiento  igual en el libro de Bancos', 'W', 'OFG', 0);

    WHEN OTHERS THEN
      CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
  END;
  END IF;
                ELSE
                  RAISE NO_DATA_FOUND;
                END IF;
END;

/* CGHP$CALL_HELP_FORM */
BEGIN
  :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := '';
  IF (:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE IS NULL) THEN
    qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(23, 'Falta el fichero de ayuda o es incorrecto'), 'W', 'OFG', 23);
  ELSE
    :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HPATH || '';
    BEGIN
      CGHP$CALL_MS_HELP(0 ,:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE);
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
  END IF;
END;

/* CGUV$CHK_KEYS_ON_VAL_FLD */
BEGIN
          IF (    name_in('LBR.CMP_FECHA') IS NOT NULL
              OR name_in('LBR.CNTBNC_TIPO') IS NOT NULL
              OR name_in('LBR.ESTADO') IS NOT NULL
              OR name_in('LBR.CNTBNC_NUMERO') IS NOT NULL
              OR name_in('LBR.TPOMVM_CODIGO') IS NOT NULL
              OR name_in('LBR.FECHA') IS NOT NULL
              OR name_in('LBR.DEBE') IS NOT NULL
              OR name_in('LBR.HABER') IS NOT NULL
              OR name_in('LBR.DESCRIPCION') IS NOT NULL
              OR name_in('LBR.NUMERO_DOCUMENTO') IS NOT NULL
              OR name_in('LBR.CMP_TIPO') IS NOT NULL
              OR name_in('LBR.CMP_CLAVE') IS NOT NULL
              OR name_in('LBR.CNTBNC_EMP_CODIGO') IS NOT NULL) THEN
  IF (    name_in('LBR.CMP_FECHA') IS NOT NULL
      AND name_in('LBR.ESTADO') IS NOT NULL
      AND name_in('LBR.TPOMVM_CODIGO') IS NOT NULL
      AND name_in('LBR.FECHA') IS NOT NULL
      AND name_in('LBR.DEBE') IS NOT NULL
      AND name_in('LBR.HABER') IS NOT NULL
      AND name_in('LBR.DESCRIPCION') IS NOT NULL
      AND name_in('LBR.NUMERO_DOCUMENTO') IS NOT NULL
      AND name_in('LBR.CMP_TIPO') IS NOT NULL
      AND name_in('LBR.CMP_CLAVE') IS NOT NULL) THEN
  BEGIN
    CGUV$CHK_LBR_UK(
      :LBR.CMP_CLAVE
     ,:LBR.CMP_TIPO
     ,:LBR.NUMERO_DOCUMENTO
     ,:LBR.DESCRIPCION
     ,:LBR.HABER
     ,:LBR.DEBE
     ,:LBR.FECHA
     ,:LBR.ESTADO
     ,:LBR.CMP_FECHA
     ,:LBR.CNTBNC_TIPO
     ,:LBR.CNTBNC_NUMERO
     ,:LBR.CNTBNC_EMP_CODIGO
     ,:LBR.NUMERO
     ,:LBR.TPOMVM_CODIGO
     ,:SYSTEM.RECORD_STATUS );
    qms$forms_errors.push('Ya existe un momimiento  igual en el libro de Bancos', 'W', 'OFG', 0);
  EXCEPTION
    WHEN NO_DATA_FOUND THEN NULL;
    WHEN OTHERS THEN
      CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
  END;
  END IF;
          ELSE
            RAISE NO_DATA_FOUND;
          END IF;
END;
       * Ejecutar en Modo de Ingreso de Consulta     No
       * Jerarquía de Ejecución                      Antes
       * Desplegar en 'Ayuda de Teclado'             Sí
       - Texto de 'Ayuda de Teclado'                 
       - Pasos de Trigger                            
       ----------
       * Nombre                                      KEY-HELP
       - Información de Subclase                     
       - Comentarios                                 
       - Estilo de Trigger                           PL/SQL
       * Texto de Trigger

/* CGAP$OLES_SEQUENCE_BEFORE */

/* CGUV$CHK_KEYS_ON_VAL_FLD */
BEGIN
    IF (    name_in('LBR.CMP_FECHA') IS NOT NULL
        OR name_in('LBR.CNTBNC_TIPO') IS NOT NULL
        OR name_in('LBR.ESTADO') IS NOT NULL
        OR name_in('LBR.CNTBNC_NUMERO') IS NOT NULL
        OR name_in('LBR.TPOMVM_CODIGO') IS NOT NULL
        OR name_in('LBR.FECHA') IS NOT NULL
        OR name_in('LBR.DEBE') IS NOT NULL
        OR name_in('LBR.HABER') IS NOT NULL
        OR name_in('LBR.DESCRIPCION') IS NOT NULL
        OR name_in('LBR.NUMERO_DOCUMENTO') IS NOT NULL
        OR name_in('LBR.CMP_TIPO') IS NOT NULL
        OR name_in('LBR.CMP_CLAVE') IS NOT NULL
        OR name_in('LBR.CNTBNC_EMP_CODIGO') IS NOT NULL) THEN
  IF (    name_in('LBR.CMP_FECHA') IS NOT NULL
      AND name_in('LBR.ESTADO') IS NOT NULL
      AND name_in('LBR.TPOMVM_CODIGO') IS NOT NULL
      AND name_in('LBR.FECHA') IS NOT NULL
      AND name_in('LBR.DEBE') IS NOT NULL
      AND name_in('LBR.HABER') IS NOT NULL
      AND name_in('LBR.DESCRIPCION') IS NOT NULL
      AND name_in('LBR.NUMERO_DOCUMENTO') IS NOT NULL
      AND name_in('LBR.CMP_TIPO') IS NOT NULL
      AND name_in('LBR.CMP_CLAVE') IS NOT NULL) THEN
  BEGIN
    CGUV$CHK_LBR_UK(
      :LBR.CMP_CLAVE
     ,:LBR.CMP_TIPO
     ,:LBR.NUMERO_DOCUMENTO
     ,:LBR.DESCRIPCION
     ,:LBR.HABER
     ,:LBR.DEBE
     ,:LBR.FECHA
     ,:LBR.ESTADO
     ,:LBR.CMP_FECHA
     ,:LBR.CNTBNC_TIPO
     ,:LBR.CNTBNC_NUMERO
     ,:LBR.CNTBNC_EMP_CODIGO
     ,:LBR.NUMERO
     ,:LBR.TPOMVM_CODIGO
     ,:SYSTEM.RECORD_STATUS );
    qms$forms_errors.push('Ya existe un momimiento  igual en el libro de Bancos', 'W', 'OFG', 0);
  EXCEPTION
    WHEN NO_DATA_FOUND THEN NULL;
    WHEN OTHERS THEN
      CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
  END;
  END IF;
    ELSE
      RAISE NO_DATA_FOUND;
    END IF;
END;
       * Ejecutar en Modo de Ingreso de Consulta     No
       * Jerarquía de Ejecución                      Antes
       * Desplegar en 'Ayuda de Teclado'             Sí
       - Texto de 'Ayuda de Teclado'                 
       - Pasos de Trigger                            
       ----------
       * Nombre                                      KEY-HELP
       - Información de Subclase                     
       - Comentarios                                 
       - Estilo de Trigger                           PL/SQL
       * Texto de Trigger                            

/* CGHP$CALL_HELP_FORM */
BEGIN
  :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := '';
  IF (:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE IS NULL) THEN
    qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(23, 'Falta el fichero de ayuda o es incorrecto'), 'W', 'OFG', 23);
  ELSE
    :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HPATH || '';
    BEGIN
      CGHP$CALL_MS_HELP(0 ,:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE);
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
  END IF;
END;
       * Ejecutar en Modo de Ingreso de Consulta     Sí
       * Jerarquía de Ejecución                      Antes
       * Desplegar en 'Ayuda de Teclado'             Sí
       - Texto de 'Ayuda de Teclado'                 
       - Pasos de Trigger                            
       ----------
       * Nombre                                      WHEN-LIST-CHANGED
       - Información de Subclase                     
       - Comentarios                                 
       - Estilo de Trigger                           PL/SQL
       * Texto de Trigger                            

-- Si se registra el movimiento como conciliado, debe registrarse el usuario y la fecha
BEGIN
   IF :LBR.ESTADO IS NOT NULL THEN
/*      IF :LBR.ESTADO = 'A' THEN
        IF :LBR.FECHA < SYSDATE-60 THEN
            QMS$ERRORS.SHOW_MESSAGE('BNC-00025',TO_CHAR(SYSDATE-60,'DD/MM/YYYY'));
        END IF;
      END IF;*/
      IF :LBR.ESTADO = 'C' THEN
         :LBR.FECHA_CONCILIACION := :LBR.FECHA;
         :LBR.USUARIO_CONCILIA := :LBR.USUARIO_CREA;
      ELSE
         :LBR.FECHA_CONCILIACION := NULL;
         :LBR.USUARIO_CONCILIA := NULL;
      END IF;
   END IF;
END;

/* CGHP$CALL_HELP_FORM */
BEGIN
  :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := '';
  IF (:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE IS NULL) THEN
    qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(23, 'Falta el fichero de ayuda o es incorrecto'), 'W', 'OFG', 23);
  ELSE
    :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HPATH || '';
    BEGIN
      CGHP$CALL_MS_HELP(0 ,:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE);
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
  END IF;
END;

/* CGAP$OLES_SEQUENCE_BEFORE */
begin

BEGIN
DECLARE
-- Fija los parámetros para generar el reporte
   pl_id ParamList;
BEGIN
   pl_id := Get_Parameter_List('PARAMETRO');
   IF NOT Id_Null(pl_id) THEN
      Destroy_Parameter_List( pl_id );
   END IF;
   pl_id := Create_Parameter_List('PARAMETRO');
   Add_Parameter(pl_id,'VCIUDAD',TEXT_PARAMETER,:GLOBAL.CIUDAD);
   Add_Parameter(pl_id,'DFECHA',TEXT_PARAMETER,TO_CHAR(:LBR.FECHA,'DD/MM/YYYY'));
   Add_Parameter(pl_id,'VBENEFICIARIO',TEXT_PARAMETER,:LBR.DESCRIPCION);
   Add_Parameter(pl_id,'NVALOR',TEXT_PARAMETER,:LBR.HABER);
   Add_Parameter(pl_id,'PARAMFORM',TEXT_PARAMETER,'NO');
   Add_Parameter(pl_id,'DESTYPE',TEXT_PARAMETER,'Printer');
   Run_Product(REPORTS,:CNTBNC.REPORTE,SYNCHRONOUS,RUNTIME,FILESYSTEM, pl_id, NULL);
END;
END;

/* CGFK$WVI_CLR_DEPS_OVF */
BEGIN
  IF (name_in('LBR.CNTBNC_EMP_CODIGO') IS NULL AND name_in('LBR.CMP_TIPO') IS NULL) THEN
    IF (:SYSTEM.RECORD_STATUS = 'NEW') THEN
      RETURN;
    END IF;
    BEGIN
      CGSF$CLRLU_LBR_LBR_TPOCMPEMP_F;
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
  END IF;
END;

/* CGUV$CHK_KEYS_ON_VAL_FLD */
BEGIN
                  IF (    name_in('LBR.CMP_FECHA') IS NOT NULL
                      OR name_in('LBR.CNTBNC_TIPO') IS NOT NULL
                      OR name_in('LBR.ESTADO') IS NOT NULL
                      OR name_in('LBR.CNTBNC_NUMERO') IS NOT NULL
                      OR name_in('LBR.TPOMVM_CODIGO') IS NOT NULL
                      OR name_in('LBR.FECHA') IS NOT NULL
                      OR name_in('LBR.DEBE') IS NOT NULL
                      OR name_in('LBR.HABER') IS NOT NULL
                      OR name_in('LBR.DESCRIPCION') IS NOT NULL
                      OR name_in('LBR.NUMERO_DOCUMENTO') IS NOT NULL
                      OR name_in('LBR.CMP_TIPO') IS NOT NULL
                      OR name_in('LBR.CMP_CLAVE') IS NOT NULL
                      OR name_in('LBR.CNTBNC_EMP_CODIGO') IS NOT NULL) THEN
  IF (    name_in('LBR.CMP_FECHA') IS NOT NULL
      AND name_in('LBR.ESTADO') IS NOT NULL
      AND name_in('LBR.TPOMVM_CODIGO') IS NOT NULL
      AND name_in('LBR.FECHA') IS NOT NULL
      AND name_in('LBR.DEBE') IS NOT NULL
      AND name_in('LBR.HABER') IS NOT NULL
      AND name_in('LBR.DESCRIPCION') IS NOT NULL
      AND name_in('LBR.NUMERO_DOCUMENTO') IS NOT NULL
      AND name_in('LBR.CMP_TIPO') IS NOT NULL
      AND name_in('LBR.CMP_CLAVE') IS NOT NULL) THEN
  BEGIN
    CGUV$CHK_LBR_UK(
      :LBR.CMP_CLAVE
     ,:LBR.CMP_TIPO
     ,:LBR.NUMERO_DOCUMENTO
     ,:LBR.DESCRIPCION
     ,:LBR.HABER
     ,:LBR.DEBE
     ,:LBR.FECHA
     ,:LBR.ESTADO
     ,:LBR.CMP_FECHA
     ,:LBR.CNTBNC_TIPO
     ,:LBR.CNTBNC_NUMERO
     ,:LBR.CNTBNC_EMP_CODIGO
     ,:LBR.NUMERO
     ,:LBR.TPOMVM_CODIGO
     ,:SYSTEM.RECORD_STATUS );
    qms$forms_errors.push('Ya existe un momimiento  igual en el libro de Bancos', 'W', 'OFG', 0);
  EXCEPTION
    WHEN NO_DATA_FOUND THEN NULL;
    WHEN OTHERS THEN
      CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
  END;
  END IF;
                  ELSE
                    RAISE NO_DATA_FOUND;
                  END IF;
END;
       * Ejecutar en Modo de Ingreso de Consulta     No
       * Jerarquía de Ejecución                      Antes
       * Desplegar en 'Ayuda de Teclado'             Sí

BEGIN

  IF (:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE IS NULL) THEN
    qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(23, 'Falta el fichero de ayuda o es incorrecto'), 'W', 'OFG', 23);
  ELSE
    :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HPATH || '';
    BEGIN
      CGHP$CALL_MS_HELP(0 ,:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE);
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
  END IF;
END;

/* CGUV$CHK_KEYS_ON_VAL_FLD */
BEGIN
                    IF (    name_in('LBR.CMP_FECHA') IS NOT NULL
                        OR name_in('LBR.CNTBNC_TIPO') IS NOT NULL
                        OR name_in('LBR.ESTADO') IS NOT NULL
                        OR name_in('LBR.CNTBNC_NUMERO') IS NOT NULL
                        OR name_in('LBR.TPOMVM_CODIGO') IS NOT NULL
                        OR name_in('LBR.FECHA') IS NOT NULL
                        OR name_in('LBR.DEBE') IS NOT NULL
                        OR name_in('LBR.HABER') IS NOT NULL
                        OR name_in('LBR.DESCRIPCION') IS NOT NULL
                        OR name_in('LBR.NUMERO_DOCUMENTO') IS NOT NULL
                        OR name_in('LBR.CMP_TIPO') IS NOT NULL
                        OR name_in('LBR.CMP_CLAVE') IS NOT NULL
                        OR name_in('LBR.CNTBNC_EMP_CODIGO') IS NOT NULL) THEN
  IF (    name_in('LBR.CMP_FECHA') IS NOT NULL
      AND name_in('LBR.ESTADO') IS NOT NULL
      AND name_in('LBR.TPOMVM_CODIGO') IS NOT NULL
      AND name_in('LBR.FECHA') IS NOT NULL
      AND name_in('LBR.DEBE') IS NOT NULL
      AND name_in('LBR.HABER') IS NOT NULL
      AND name_in('LBR.DESCRIPCION') IS NOT NULL
      AND name_in('LBR.NUMERO_DOCUMENTO') IS NOT NULL
      AND name_in('LBR.CMP_TIPO') IS NOT NULL
      AND name_in('LBR.CMP_CLAVE') IS NOT NULL) THEN
  BEGIN
    CGUV$CHK_LBR_UK(
      :LBR.CMP_CLAVE
     ,:LBR.CMP_TIPO
     ,:LBR.NUMERO_DOCUMENTO
     ,:LBR.DESCRIPCION
     ,:LBR.HABER
     ,:LBR.DEBE
     ,:LBR.FECHA
     ,:LBR.ESTADO
     ,:LBR.CMP_FECHA
     ,:LBR.CNTBNC_TIPO
     ,:LBR.CNTBNC_NUMERO
     ,:LBR.CNTBNC_EMP_CODIGO
     ,:LBR.NUMERO
     ,:LBR.TPOMVM_CODIGO
     ,:SYSTEM.RECORD_STATUS );
    qms$forms_errors.push('Ya existe un momimiento  igual en el libro de Bancos', 'W', 'OFG', 0);
  EXCEPTION
    WHEN NO_DATA_FOUND THEN NULL;
    WHEN OTHERS THEN
      CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
  END;
  END IF;
                    ELSE
                      RAISE NO_DATA_FOUND;
                    END IF;
END;

BEGIN
-- Llama al procedimiento que permite
-- contabilizar un movimiento de Bancos
DECLARE
CONTADOR NUMBER;
NOMBRE_SEC VARCHAR2(30);
BEGIN
   SET_BLOCK_PROPERTY('LBR',UPDATE_ALLOWED,PROPERTY_TRUE);
   :LBR.LBR_IND := NULL;
   IF :LBR.CMP_FECHA IS NULL THEN
      :LBR.CMP_FECHA := :LBR.FECHA;
   END IF;
  IF :LBR.CMP_TIPO IS NULL OR :LBR.CMP_FECHA IS NULL THEN
       QMS$ERRORS.SHOW_MESSAGE('El Tipo/Número de Comprobante no debe ser nulo');
  END IF;

--   IF :LBR.CMP_TIPO IS NOT NULL AND :LBR.CMP_CLAVE IS NOT NULL  AND :LBR.CMP_FECHA IS NOT NULL THEN
--      SELECT NVL(COUNT(CLAVE),0) INTO CONTADOR
--      FROM  COMPROBANTES
--      WHERE TPOCMPEMP_EMP_CODIGO = :GLOBAL.CG$EMPRESA_CODIGO AND
--            TPOCMPEMP_TPOCMP_CODIGO = :LBR.CMP_TIPO AND
--            FECHA = :LBR.CMP_FECHA AND
--            CLAVE = :LBR.CMP_CLAVE ;
--      IF CONTADOR > 0 THEN
--         QMS$ERRORS.SHOW_MESSAGE('El comprobante Nro.'||TO_CHAR(:LBR.CMP_CLAVE)||'del'||TO_CHAR(:LBR.CMP_FECHA,'DD/MM/YYYY')|| 'ya existe');
--      ELSE
         :LBR.ESTADO_CONTABILIZA := 'C';
         :LBR.LBR_IND := 'C';
         qms$forms_errors.Add_Suppress_Message('FRM-40404');
         POST;
         qms$forms_errors.Delete_Suppress_Message('FRM-40404');
         IF :LBR.LBR_IND = 'C' THEN
            SET_BLOCK_PROPERTY('LBR',UPDATE_ALLOWED,PROPERTY_FALSE);
            SET_ITEM_PROPERTY('BTN_CONTABILIZAR',ENABLED,PROPERTY_FALSE);
            SET_ITEM_PROPERTY('BTN_COMPROBANTE',ENABLED,PROPERTY_TRUE);
            CGNV$AI_BTN_VER_COMPROBANTE;
         ELSE
            :LBR.ESTADO_CONTABILIZA := 'N';
            :LBR.LBR_IND := 'E';
         END IF;
--      END IF;
END;
END;

/* CGHP$CALL_HELP_FORM */
BEGIN
  :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := '';
  IF (:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE IS NULL) THEN
    qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(23, 'Falta el fichero de ayuda o es incorrecto'), 'W', 'OFG', 23);
  ELSE
    :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HPATH || '';
    BEGIN
      CGHP$CALL_MS_HELP(0 ,:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE);
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
  END IF;
END;

/* CGHP$CALL_HELP_FORM */
BEGIN
  :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := '';
  IF (:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE IS NULL) THEN
    qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(23, 'Falta el fichero de ayuda o es incorrecto'), 'W', 'OFG', 23);
  ELSE
    :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HPATH || '';
    BEGIN
      CGHP$CALL_MS_HELP(0 ,:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE);
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
  END IF;
END;

BEGIN
   IF :SYSTEM.RECORD_STATUS IN ('INSERT','NEW') THEN
      :LBR.TPOMVM_CODIGO := :TIPO.MOV_TIPO;
      qms$errors.show_Debug_info('EL TIPO DE MOVIMIENTO ES '||:LBR.TPOMVM_CODIGO);
      GO_ITEM('FECHA');
      Habilitar_Campos;
   END IF;
END;

Revision When       Who
         What
5.0      25-06-1998 S. Davelaar
         Headstart Template Package 5.0 BETA
5.0.1    18-08-1998 S. Davelaar
         - QMSSO$CONCEAL_ITEM added
         - CGSO$CANVAS_SPREAD now subclasses from CGSO$CANVAS_POPUP
         - QMSSO$MODAL_DOCUMENT_WINDOW added
         - parameter QMS$MENU_CALLING_FORM removed
         - triggers KEY-CLRFRM, PRE-FORM, QUERY_FIND, WHEN-NEW_BLOCK-INSTANCE,
           and WHEN-NEW-FORM-INSTANCE moved from object group QMS$STND_MODULE
           to object group QMS$MODULE
         - Lov QMS$ENABLED_LIST_LAMP changed to Record Group LOV
         - Record group QMS$ENABLE_LIST_LAMP added to object group QMS$MODULE
         - CG$LOV added (will be renamed to CGSO$LOV if OFG bug causing wrong
           LOV height to be generatedif CGSO$LOV is present, is fixed)
         - Background item VA's no longer inherit from qms$item_font (now using
           <Unspecified> setting)
         - Foreground prompt VA's no longer inherit from qms$prompt_font (now
           using <Unspecified> setting)
         - Visual attribute QMS$BOLD added
         - Visual attribute qms$gui_item_font added
         - item qms$block_info made non-navigable, and disabled
         - WHEN-WINDOW-CLOSED trigger added to QMSSO$MODULE
         - Iconic Calendar buttons now subclass QMSSO$CALENDAR_BUTTON,
           tooltips added
         - KEY-EXIT trigger added to QMSSO$MODULE
         - QMSSO$QUERY_ONLY_ITEM added
         - width and height of CGSO$WINDOW set to 1
         - Tooltip VA of QMSSO$TOOLBAR_BUTTON set to QMS$TOOLTIP
         - Fire in enter-query mode property switched on for
           WHEN-NEW-RECORD-INSTANCE trigger in QMSSO$MSEL_BLOCK (now required
           for highlighting queryable items)
         - QMSSO$NO_BEVEL_ITEM added
5.0.2    24-09-1998 S. Davelaar
         - Form level PRE-BLOCK trigger removed
         - PRE-BLOCK trigger added to CGSO$BLOCK
         - PRE-BLOCK trigger added to CGSO$BLOCK_CT
         - qms$block_info item made non-queryable, number of items displayed
           set to 1
         - QMSSO$WIZARD_BLOCK: Database Block property set to Yes
         - CONSOLE_WINDOW renamed to QMS$HIDDEN_ITEMS
         - QMSSO$TOOLBAR_WINDOW renamed to QMSSO$WEB_TOOLBAR_WINDOW
         - KEY-DOWN, KEY-UP, KEY-PRVREC, KEY-NXTREC, KEY-NXTREC added to
           QMSSO$MSEL_BLOCK
         - KEY-MENU added to QMSSO$MODULE
         - Query length set to 500 in CGSO$DEFAULT_ITEM
         - WHEN-BUTTON-PRESSED trigger now owned by all QMSSO buttons individually,
           instead of inherited with the trigger text being overridden
         - Default value of parameter SWITCH_MENU set to DO_REPLACE
         - Renamed all icons in toolbar, calendar and CGSO$LOV_BUT to have qms prefix
         - KEY-EXIT trigger moved from object group QMSSO$MODULE to QMSSO$STND_MODULE
5.0.3    03-12-1998 S. Davelaar
         - Item CGSO$DATE: maximum length changed to 11
         - Added CGSO$DATETIME subclasses CGSO$DATE overriding datatype (set to
           datetime), and maximum length (set to 20)
         - Item QMSSO$TEXT: maximum length and query length set to 2000,
           Multi-line set to Yes
         - Item CGSO$DEFAULT_ITEM: maximum length and query length set to 2000
5.0.3.1  14-01-1999 S. Davelaar
         - Parameter qmsolb50_revision renamed to objlib_revision, parameter
           objlib_name added and stored in object group QMSSO$MODULE
         - Object group QMSSO$MODULE: QMS$BLUE_FOREGROUND
         - Object group QMSSO$MODULE: Trigger KEY-HELP added
         - Object group QMSSO$MODULE: Paremeter SCHEMA_OWNER added
         - Block CGSO$BLOCK: POST-SELECT trigger added as work around for OFG
           bug 818001
         - Block CGSO$BLOCK_CT: Property query all records set to True
         - Block QMSSO$DYNAMIC_PROMPT_VALUE removed
         - Block QMSSO$WIZARD: item wizard_height added
         - Block QMSSO$WIZARD_SPLIT_BLOCK added, subclasses QMSSO$WIZARD, two
           own triggers added: ON-LOCK and WHEN-VALIDATE-RECORD
         - Visual Attribute QMS$BLUE_FOREGROUND added
         - Visual Attribute CALENDAR DISABLED: background color changed to gray
         - Visual Attribute QMS$PROMPT_LIGHT_BLUE renamed to QMS$PROMPT_LIGHTBLUE
         - Item QMSSO$TEXT: Trigger WHEN-NEW-ITEM-INSTANCE added
         - Item QMSSO$BLUE_TEXT added
         - Item QMSSO$BLUE_BOLD_TEXT: current record VA set to
           QMS$BLUE_FOREGROUND, subclasses from QMSSO$BLUE_TEXT
           trigger WHEN-TAB-PAGE-CHANGED removed
         - Item QMSSO$DISABLED_BUTTON added.
         - Tooltip property of item qms$block_info cleared in all blocks except
           QMSSO$BLOCK_MSEL
         - Items CALENDAR.OK and CALENDAR.CANCEL: Mouse navigate property set to True
         - Item CGSO$DEFAULT_ITEM: when-mouse-click trigger removed
         - Item CGSO$DEFAULT_ITEM: Tooltip text set to 'No hint available.'
           (Work around for webforms bug, to be able to show tooltips on WEB)
         - All QMSSO$ buttons: calls to qms$event_item removed from WHEN-BUTTON-
           PRESSED triggers
         - New source item QMSSO$LOV_FORM_ITEM
         - Window QMSSO$DIALOG_WINDOW: Inherit menu property set to No
         - Window CALENDAR: Inherit menu property set to No
         - Popup Menu Item HELP_CONTEXT: PL/SQL code re-inherited from parent
         - Block QMS$TOOLBAR: WHEN-BUTTON-PRESSED changed into WHEN-MOUSE-CLICK
           trigger to be able to trap right-mouse-button click (forms bug 636000)
         - Block QMS$TOOLBAR: ORDER_BY poplist added with WHEN-LIST-CHANGED trigger.

     - Visible                                       Sí
     ^ Indicio                                       Corta la selección actual y la pone en el apuntador
     ^ Descripción de Ayuda                          Removes the selected text and places it on the clipboard.  The contents of the clipboard can be pasted into text items or into other applications.  The contents of the clipboard are overwritten each time a Copy or Cut is performed.

The Copy and Cut commands are disabled when no text is selected.  The Cut command is also disabled if the current item is not updatable.

     - Código de Artículo de Menú                    

qms$menu.set_current_action('LIST');
execute_trigger('QMS$MENU_ITEM');
     - Visible                                       Sí
     ^ Indicio                                       Invoca una ventana con una lista de valores valida desde la cual escoger
     ^ Descripción de Ayuda                          Displays a list of values (LOV) which is a scrollable pop-up window that provides you with a selection list containing one or more columns with all the valid values available for the current text item.  The LOV appears in a modal window which means you cannot work in other windows when an LOV is displayed.  You can move and resize the LOV (if the runtime window manager supports doing so).  The LOV window remains displayed until you select a single value or cancel the LOV.

Use the [Up] and [Down] keys or the scroll bar to navigate through the list.  Press the OK button or the [Accept] key to choose the selected value and close the list of values window.  Press the Cancel button to leave the list without making a selection.  When you select a value, the value is automatically returned into the current item.  Using an LOV can save keystrokes during data-entry and it ensures that the value entered is valid for that item.

There are LOV auto-reduction and search features to help you locate a value in a list.  To use auto-reduction, simply type the desired entry directly in the list pane of the LOV window.  As each character is entered, the list is reduced to only those values that match the string being entered.  Pressing [Delete Backwards] expands the reduced list of choices.  Auto-reduction works by comparing the string you entered with the values in the first column displayed in the LOV.  

You can use the search feature to locate a match for a specific text string and to do wildcard searches using "" and "_".  To use the search feature, enter your search criteria string in the LOV's Find field and press the Find button to execute the search.  The list is shortened to those choices whose first column values match your search criteria.  Note that if you precede the search criteria with a "" symbol, the search will be performed using all the LOV columns.

There is also an automatic search and complete feature that may have been implemented by the form designer.  An LOV evaluates a text item's current value as a search value.  That is, if you invoke the list of values in a text item and the item already contains a value, that value is automatically used as if you had entered it into the LOV's find field to reduce the list.  If the value would reduce the list to match only one record, the LOV does not display, but automatically enters the complete value into the current item.

For date or datetime fields, a calendar window is invoked which provides easy navigation between dates, months and years and allows you to quickly enter a date (and time for datetime fields).  Calendar windows help to ensure that you enter valid dates in the correct format.  The calendar window appears showing the same month as the current date in the date field with the date highlighted.  If no date exists in the date field, the calendar displays the current month with today's date highlighted.  Today's date is also underlined.  If there is a range of dates that is not valid for this field then the form designer can disable the dates on the calendar.

To help identify when an LOV is available for an item, a "<LIST>" (or "List of Values") lamp is displayed on the status line when you navigate into the item.

This function is also available through a button on the toolbar or directly adjacent the item.


For more information about runtime item interaction and examples, see the Oracle Forms Reference manual or the Getting Started with Forms manual.

     - Comentarios                                   
     - Activado                                      Sí
     ^ Etiqueta                                      ¿&Que es esto?
     - Tipo de Artículo de Menú                      Simple
     - Artículo Mágico                               Ninguno
     - Tipo de Comando                               PL/SQL
     - Código de Artículo de Menú                    

qms$menu.set_current_action('HELP_CONTEXT');
execute_trigger('QMS$MENU_ITEM');
     - Visible                                       Sí
     ^ Indicio                                       Entra en modo de ayuda contextual
     ^ Descripción de Ayuda                          Switches the mouse pointer to a question mark "?", setting the application in help mode.  You can then click on any menu entry, button or item to get context-sensitive help.  A pop-up window will appear containing an explanation of the object.

This function is also available via the iconic help button on the toolbar.

/* CG$WHEN_NEW_FORM_INSTANCE */
PROCEDURE CG$WHEN_NEW_FORM_INSTANCE IS
BEGIN
/* CGDV$POPULATE_DYNAMIC_LISTS */

  CGDV$POPULATE_DYNAMIC_LISTS;
EXCEPTION
  WHEN OTHERS THEN
    CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
END;

/* CGSM$SHOW_STRIP_MENU */
BEGIN
  show_menu;
END;

/* CGLY$INIT_CANVASES */
BEGIN
  CGLY$CANVAS_MANAGEMENT;
END;

/* CGBS$STARTUP */
BEGIN
  default_value('A', 'GLOBAL.CG$QUERY_MODE');
  CGBS$.SET_RELATIONS( :GLOBAL.CG$QUERY_MODE );
  CGBS$SET_QUERY_MODE( :GLOBAL.CG$QUERY_MODE );
END;
END;

   * Nombre                                          CGDV$POPULATE_DYNAMIC_LISTS
   - Información de Subclase                         
   - Comentarios                                     
   * Texto de Unidad de Programa                     

/* CGDV$POPULATE_DYNAMIC_LISTS */
PROCEDURE CGDV$POPULATE_DYNAMIC_LISTS IS
  temp NUMBER;  /* Return value of populate_group call */
  rg_id RECORDGROUP;  /* Return value of populate_group call */
BEGIN
  rg_id := create_group_from_query('CGDV$DLRG',
    'select RV_MEANING, RV_LOW_VALUE '||
    'from   CG_REF_CODES '||
    'where  RV_DOMAIN = ''MONEDA'' '||
    'order by  2');
  temp := populate_group(rg_id);
  populate_list('CNTBNC.MONEDA', rg_id);
  delete_group(rg_id);

  rg_id := create_group_from_query('CGDV$DLRG',
    'select RV_MEANING, RV_LOW_VALUE '||
    'from   CG_REF_CODES '||
    'where  RV_DOMAIN = ''TARJETA DE CREDITO'' '||
    'order by  2');
  temp := populate_group(rg_id);
  populate_list('CNTBNC.CLASE_TARJETA', rg_id);
  delete_group(rg_id);

  rg_id := create_group_from_query('CGDV$DLRG',
    'select RV_MEANING, RV_LOW_VALUE '||
    'from   CG_REF_CODES '||
    'where  RV_DOMAIN = ''TIPO MOVIMIENTO'' '||
    'order by  2');
  temp := populate_group(rg_id);
  populate_list('LBR.TPOMVM_CODIGO', rg_id);
  delete_group(rg_id);

  rg_id := create_group_from_query('CGDV$DLRG',
    'select RV_MEANING, RV_LOW_VALUE '||
    'from   CG_REF_CODES '||
    'where  RV_DOMAIN = ''ESTADO MOVIMIENTO BANCOS'' '||
    'order by  2');
  temp := populate_group(rg_id);
  populate_list('LBR.ESTADO', rg_id);
  delete_group(rg_id);

  rg_id := create_group_from_query('CGDV$DLRG',
    'select RV_MEANING, RV_LOW_VALUE '||
    'from   CG_REF_CODES '||
    'where  RV_DOMAIN = ''TIPO MOVIMIENTO'' '||
    'order by  2');
  temp := populate_group(rg_id);
  populate_list('TIPO.MOV_TIPO', rg_id);
  delete_group(rg_id);

END;
   - Tipo de Unidad de Programa                      Message 8393 not found;  product=forms50; facility=FMD

/* CGFK$QRY_CNTBNC_CNTBNC_ENTFNC_ */
PROCEDURE CGFK$QRY_CNTBNC_CNTBNC_ENTFNC_(
   P_NOMBRE        IN OUT VARCHAR2
  ,P_ENTFNC_CODIGO IN     NUMBER  ) IS
BEGIN
  DECLARE
    CURSOR C IS
      select ENTFNC.NOMBRE
      from   ENTIDADES_FINANCIERAS ENTFNC
      where  ENTFNC.CODIGO = P_ENTFNC_CODIGO;
  BEGIN
    OPEN C;
    FETCH C
    into    P_NOMBRE;
    IF COTFOUND THEN
      CLOSE C;
      RAISE NO_DATA_FOUND;
    END IF;
    CLOSE C;
  END;
END;
   - Tipo de Unidad de Programa                      Message 8393 not found;  product=forms50; facility=FMD

/* CGFK$QRY_LBR_LBR_TPOMVM_FK */
PROCEDURE CGFK$QRY_LBR_LBR_TPOMVM_FK(
   P_ESTADO_DE_DISPONIBILIDAD IN OUT VARCHAR2
  ,P_INGRESA_REFERENCIA       IN OUT VARCHAR2
  ,P_CONTABILIZACION          IN OUT VARCHAR2
  ,P_APLICABLE                IN OUT VARCHAR2
  ,P_OPERACION                IN OUT VARCHAR2
  ,P_TPOMVM_CODIGO            IN     VARCHAR2) IS
BEGIN
  DECLARE
    CURSOR C IS
      select TPOMVM.OPERACION
            ,TPOMVM.APLICABLE
            ,TPOMVM.CONTABILIZACION
            ,TPOMVM.INGRESA_REFERENCIA
            ,TPOMVM.ESTADO_DE_DISPONIBILIDAD
      from   TIPOS_DE_MOVIMIENTOS TPOMVM
      where  TPOMVM.CODIGO = P_TPOMVM_CODIGO;
  BEGIN
    OPEN C;
    FETCH C
    into    P_OPERACION
          , P_APLICABLE
          , P_CONTABILIZACION
          , P_INGRESA_REFERENCIA
          , P_ESTADO_DE_DISPONIBILIDAD;
    IF COTFOUND THEN
      CLOSE C;
      RAISE NO_DATA_FOUND;
    END IF;
    CLOSE C;
  END;
END;

   - Información de Subclase

/* CGFK$CHK_LBR_LBR_TPOMVM_FK */
PROCEDURE CGFK$CHK_LBR_LBR_TPOMVM_FK(
   P_ESTADO_DE_DISPONIBILIDAD IN OUT VARCHAR2
  ,P_INGRESA_REFERENCIA       IN OUT VARCHAR2
  ,P_CONTABILIZACION          IN OUT VARCHAR2
  ,P_APLICABLE                IN OUT VARCHAR2
  ,P_OPERACION                IN OUT VARCHAR2
  ,P_TPOMVM_CODIGO            IN     VARCHAR2) IS
BEGIN
  DECLARE
    CURSOR C IS
      select TPOMVM.OPERACION
            ,TPOMVM.APLICABLE
            ,TPOMVM.CONTABILIZACION
            ,TPOMVM.INGRESA_REFERENCIA
            ,TPOMVM.ESTADO_DE_DISPONIBILIDAD
      from   TIPOS_DE_MOVIMIENTOS TPOMVM
      where  TPOMVM.CODIGO = P_TPOMVM_CODIGO
      and    TPOMVM.CONTABILIZACION NOT IN ('N','S');
  BEGIN
    OPEN C;
    FETCH C
    into    P_OPERACION
          , P_APLICABLE
          , P_CONTABILIZACION
          , P_INGRESA_REFERENCIA
          , P_ESTADO_DE_DISPONIBILIDAD;
    IF COTFOUND THEN
      CLOSE C;
      RAISE NO_DATA_FOUND;
    END IF;
    CLOSE C;
  END;
END;

/* CGSF$CLRLU_LBR_LBR_TPOMVM_FK */
PROCEDURE CGSF$CLRLU_LBR_LBR_TPOMVM_FK IS
BEGIN
  IF (:LBR.TPOMVM_CODIGO IS NOT NULL) THEN
    :LBR.TPOMVM_CODIGO := NULL;
  END IF;
  IF (:LBR.OPERACION IS NOT NULL) THEN
    :LBR.OPERACION := NULL;
  END IF;
  IF (:LBR.APLICABLE IS NOT NULL) THEN
    :LBR.APLICABLE := NULL;
  END IF;
  IF (:LBR.CONTABILIZACION IS NOT NULL) THEN
    :LBR.CONTABILIZACION := NULL;
  END IF;
  IF (:LBR.INGRESA_REFERENCIA IS NOT NULL) THEN
    :LBR.INGRESA_REFERENCIA := NULL;
  END IF;
  IF (:LBR.ESTADO_DE_DISPONIBILIDAD IS NOT NULL) THEN
    :LBR.ESTADO_DE_DISPONIBILIDAD := NULL;
  END IF;
END;
   - Tipo de Unidad de Programa                      Message 8393 not found;  product=forms50; facility=FMD
